dataIdInfo.idPurp: Administrative Level 3 COD dataset for IRQ.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from an email from the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated Admin0 name and p-code fields. 2. Created and populated reference name field. 3. As instructed by IMO, p-codes have been reconstructed to have standard widths and now use ISO code "IQ". 4. Trailing space removed from Admin2 name "Al-Baaj ". 5. Fixed nesting error with Admin3 "Al-Zab" and Admin1 "Kirkuk". 6. Trailing space removed from Admin3 name "Markaz Derbendikhan ". 7. Admin3 names "Kadr karam" and "MakkHoul" were made Proper Case. 8. Fixed an error where the Admin2 and 3 Arabic names were swapped for Admin3 "Markaz Rawanduz". Its Admin3 Arabic name is now "مركز راوندوز" and its Admin2 Arabic name is "راوندوز".
